Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:08.75,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:186620,188755}I expect all of you\Nto take this with the upmost severity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.69,0:03:11.05,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:189690,191058}I am counting on you,\Ngentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:12.42,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:191358,192426}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.46,0:03:22.23,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:200467,202235}Andréa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.23,0:03:24.17,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:202235,204171}Be honest with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.17,0:03:26.27,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:204171,206273}What are our chances of win?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:29.27,Default,Andréa,0,0,0,,{TIME:206273,209276}I don't know. But what I know is\Nthat losing is not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:33.98,Default,Andréa,0,0,0,,{TIME:210711,213980}Back in Paris, I have\Nmy parents and two sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:37.61,Default,Andréa,0,0,0,,{TIME:213980,217617}I cannot put my family at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:17.52,Default,Marie,0,0,0,,{TIME:255455,257524}Darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:19.45,Default,Marie,0,0,0,,{TIME:257524,259459}Settle down a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:21.52,Default,Léon,0,0,0,,{TIME:260427,261528}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:26.73,Default,Marie,0,0,0,,{TIME:263296,266733}You don't have\Nto worry about Isabelle.
