Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:44.81,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:283083,284818}Did you find Ms. Isabelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:47.85,Default,Maid,0,0,0,,{TIME:284818,287854}Yes, she's playing\Nat the fountain in the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:50.95,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:288421,290957}She doesn't think of us at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.95,0:04:53.99,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:290957,293994}Make her stop whatever she's doing,\Nand let's prepare her for the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:55.66,Default,Maid,0,0,0,,{TIME:294361,295662}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:02.73,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:298565,302736}Today she is supposed to make her social\Ndebut. What a troublesome little lady…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:09.70,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:307574,309709}I don't wanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:12.31,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:309709,312312}This thing is way too tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:15.71,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:312312,315715}Ms. Isabelle has become\Nvery beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:17.81,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:315715,317818}Take a look in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:20.35,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:317818,320353}You're no longer that\Nmischievous little tomboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:37.53,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:335068,337537}This is… me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:40.30,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:337537,340307}That's right.\NYou're an elegant lady now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:44.74,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:341675,344744}{\i1}An elegant… lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:05:59.59,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:358258,359593}{\i1}An elegant lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:18.44,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:373506,378445}Tell me, Jeanne, who is the\Nfairer maiden, me, or my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.91,0:06:21.28,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:378912,381281}Compared to Ms. Geneviève?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:23.88,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:381882,383884}Oh, that look says it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:25.51,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:383884,385518}Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:28.02,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:385518,388021}My sister is in another\Nleague, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.02,0:06:29.65,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:388021,389656}What ever was I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:32.15,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:390090,392158}No, that's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:35.06,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:392158,395061}Ms. Geneviève has her elegance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:37.93,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:395061,397931}However, you, Ms. Isabelle\Nhave your young age.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:39.56,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:397931,399566}It's a good weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:41.23,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:400000,401234}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:43.43,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:401234,403436}I could get used to such flattery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:47.40,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:404971,407407}It's not flattery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:48.64,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:407407,408642}Right, girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.17,Default,Maid,0,0,0,,{TIME:408642,410176}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:52.81,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:410610,412812}All right, let me\Nshow myself to my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:56.61,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:415015,416616}I wonder what she'll say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:03.18,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:419853,423189}Oh, dear. She's still such a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:23.84,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:441741,443843}Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:26.78,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:444611,446780}Sister, take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:28.94,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:447280,448949}Oh? Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:34.15,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:452085,454154}Look what I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:35.28,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:454154,455288}Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:38.45,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:455288,458458}When you wear a dress for a party, you need\Nto make more careful movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:44.99,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:460360,464998}Here I am, finally trying\Nto show you something nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:46.19,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:464998,466199}I'm such a klutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:47.80,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:466199,467801}That is not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:50.03,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:467801,470036}Isabelle, you're very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:52.87,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:470503,472872}Do you really think so?\NThank you, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:56.47,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:472872,476476}By the way, Maestro, are you going\Nto the ball with us today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:07:59.91,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:476676,479913}Yes, I will play\Nthe piano this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.31,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:480046,482315}I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:09.95,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:482782,489956}Isabelle, why don't you show your\Nwonderful dress to Mother and Father now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:13.42,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:489956,493426}I need to continue\Nwith my piano lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:22.83,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:497597,502836}Mother and Father have been eagerly\Nwaiting for you all this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:25.33,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:503636,505338}You're right.\NI'm sorry I disturbed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:28.97,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:507941,508975}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:32.21,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:508975,512212}Oops, that won't do.\NI'm a proper lady now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:36.04,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:514614,516049}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:43.52,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:520186,523523}That brings memories.\NShe makes me remember my own past.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:46.39,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:524391,526393}The day I made my social debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:49.02,Default,Jules,0,0,0,,{TIME:527027,529029}Social debuts and balls?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:52.83,Default,Jules,0,0,0,,{TIME:529029,532832}France is now\Nin the middle of a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.83,0:08:55.86,Default,Jules,0,0,0,,{TIME:532832,535869}I don't understand\Nwhat the rich are thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.13,0:09:00.54,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:539139,540540}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:03.27,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:540774,543276}But, Jules…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:06.41,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:543276,546413}The feeling of love\Nremains constant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.51,0:09:10.05,Default,Jules,0,0,0,,{TIME:547514,550050}Let's not go in\Nthat direction, Geneviève.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:14.55,Default,Jules,0,0,0,,{TIME:551017,554554}I'm nothing but a poor piano teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:16.32,Default,Jules,0,0,0,,{TIME:554554,556322}The worlds we live in\Nare too different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:18.05,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:556556,558058}Jules…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.05,0:09:21.16,Default,Jules,0,0,0,,{TIME:558058,561161}Besides, you have\Nan ideal fiancé, Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:24.03,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:561161,564030}That was my Father's decision.\NYou are the one I'm in love with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:25.23,Default,Jules,0,0,0,,{TIME:564030,565231}Geneviève!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:27.46,Default,Jules,0,0,0,,{TIME:565732,567467}Some mountains\Ncannot be climbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:28.40,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:567467,568401}I will not accept that.
Comment: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:23.59,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:623590,623590}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:40.84,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:639372,640840}{\i1}A social debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:43.44,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:640840,643443}{\i1}She was about to meet\Nthe high society for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:49.14,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:643443,649149}{\i1}Isabelle couldn't suppress her heart beat,\Nfull of expectations and anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:54.78,Default,Marie,0,0,0,,{TIME:652952,654787}We will be there any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:57.89,Default,Marie,0,0,0,,{TIME:655722,657891}There is no need\Nto feel stiff, Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:20.34,Default,Gaston,0,0,0,,{TIME:678711,680346}We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:28.58,Default,Léon,0,0,0,,{TIME:685318,688588}This evening is your first step\Ninto high society, Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:30.59,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:688588,690590}Thank you, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:41.43,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:698965,701434}Mother, I'm anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:46.57,Default,Marie,0,0,0,,{TIME:704070,706573}My dear Isabelle.\NI was just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:48.80,Default,Marie,0,0,0,,{TIME:706573,708808}Where has your\Nusual bravery gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:50.94,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:709676,710944}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.34,0:11:53.54,Default,Gaston,0,0,0,,{TIME:711344,713546}Please take my hand,\NMs. Geneviève.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.74,0:11:55.38,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:713746,715381}Thank you, Gaston.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.28,0:11:57.75,Default,Léon,0,0,0,,{TIME:716282,717750}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:02.22,Default,Gaston,0,0,0,,{TIME:720153,722222}{\i1}Ms. Geneviève…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:10.66,Default,Gaston,0,0,0,,{TIME:728728,730663}{\i1}Ms. Geneviève.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:28.34,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:744611,748348}Léon and Marie Rostain\Nwith their daughters!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:51.77,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:769669,771771}This is the high society…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:54.54,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:771771,774540}{\i1}This is the high society, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:58.61,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:775408,778611}{\i1}From the moment of her\Ndebut in the high society,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:01.94,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:778611,781948}{\i1}Isabelle's beauty\Ncaptured people's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:05.21,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:783683,785218}You're so beautiful, Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:07.55,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:786319,787553}Mr. Victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:09.92,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:788187,789922}You have grown into a fine lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:15.82,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:792558,795828}Tell me, Isabelle,\Nwould you say yes to a dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:19.29,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:795828,799299}Or am I not worthy,\Nas your sister's fiancé?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:22.26,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:799599,802268}No, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:23.77,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:802268,803770}Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:25.07,Default,Léon,0,0,0,,{TIME:803770,805071}You can dance with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:29.94,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:808241,809942}Here, Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:32.81,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:811444,812812}Oh… Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:38.08,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:816549,818084}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:14:01.40,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:838237,841407}{\i1}That dance was\Nlike a dream for Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.37,0:14:11.08,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:842375,851084}{\i1}Isabelle was strangely attracted\Nto her sister Geneviève's fiancé, Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:22.29,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:860560,862295}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:23.86,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:862295,863863}May I have a dance now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.63,0:14:27.20,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:865631,867200}You will be drafted soon as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:30.20,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:867633,870203}I shall go back to my fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:31.73,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:870203,871738}Victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:37.91,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:876542,877910}Victor…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:42.71,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:879212,882715}Isabelle, what's wrong?\NDid you forget about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:45.88,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:883049,885885}You bullied me all the time\Nwhen we were kids, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.88,0:14:48.62,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:885885,888621}We lived next to each other\Nin Versailles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:50.52,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:889122,890523}Jean!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:52.19,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:890523,892191}It's you, Jean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:57.96,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:896295,897964}{\i1}This is dangerous!\NI'm going to fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:02.50,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:900166,902502}{\i1}Wait for me! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:11.47,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:909542,911477}{\i1}What a big catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:15.24,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:913279,915248}{\i1}It's so tiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.04,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:915581,917049}{\i1}Jean, I'll give you one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:18.25,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:917049,918251}{\i1}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.08,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:918251,919085}{\i1}Catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:21.58,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:920620,921587}{\i1}Owie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.39,0:15:26.42,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:924390,926426}{\i1}You're so weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:30.79,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:927093,930797}{\i1}Hey, Isabelle, will you be\Nmy bride when we grow up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:32.73,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:930797,932732}{\i1}Me, Jean's bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:34.23,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:932732,934233}{\i1}Fat chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:36.56,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:934400,936569}{\i1}No way…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:41.04,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:936569,941040}{\i1}Who would want to marry\Na weakling like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:46.11,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:941040,946112}{\i1}What do you know?\NIsabelle, you'll become my bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:49.11,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:947013,949115}{\i1}Get off your high horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:15:59.72,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:958357,959725}Jean…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:02.02,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:959725,962028}You're that crybaby?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:05.93,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:962028,965932}That's right. Isabelle, do you remember\Nwhen I asked you to marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:07.96,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:966499,967967}I've completely forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:09.80,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:967967,969802}Oh, what a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:14.17,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:969802,974173}Listen, Jean. Tonight, I've made\Nmy debut into the high society.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:16.30,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:974173,976309}I can't play kids games\Nwith you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:18.31,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:976976,978311}Won't you dance with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:20.71,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:978578,980713}Not in a hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:23.48,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:981347,983483}She hasn't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:24.88,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:983483,984884}Ha, that girl's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:26.88,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:984884,986886}Oh, do you really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.18,Default,Léon,0,0,0,,{TIME:988921,990189}Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:33.39,Default,Léon,0,0,0,,{TIME:990189,993392}It's been two years since\Nyour engagement to Geneviève.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:37.59,Default,Léon,0,0,0,,{TIME:993392,997597}Now that you are an army captain,\Njust like my son Andréa,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:40.43,Default,Léon,0,0,0,,{TIME:997597,1000433}you've fully met the expectations\NI've set for my daughter's husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:43.10,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000433,1003102}Mr. Rostain. Even though the aristocratic\Nworld is always dazzling,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:44.80,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003102,1004804}France is now in war.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:48.94,Default,Léon,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005371,1008941}But it is evident\Nthat we will win this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:51.41,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009976,1011410}I am a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:53.64,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011410,1013646}Andréa is fighting\Non the battlefield as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:57.01,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014046,1017016}I cannot selfishly seek happiness\Nin such a difficult time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:17:01.42,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017483,1021420}When this war is over,\NI will marry Geneviève.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:05.95,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023389,1025958}{\i1}A marriage with Victor…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:07.52,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025958,1027527}{\i1}But Jules…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:10.09,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027527,1030096}{\i1}What about Jules?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:15.33,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030096,1035334}{\i1}Geneviève wanted to escape\Nfrom the brilliant ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:27.64,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046412,1047647}Let us dance, Geneviève.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.64,0:17:28.54,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047647,1048548}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.35,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050116,1051350}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:04.15,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078611,1084150}{\i1}Victor could not imagine in his\Nworst nightmares that his fiancée Geneviève
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.15,0:18:06.71,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084150,1086719}{\i1}could be in love\Nwith another man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:11.92,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088721,1091924}{\i1}Geneviève… You're so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.29,0:18:15.82,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093292,1095828}{\i1}Jules… I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.27,0:18:32.14,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109275,1112144}{\i1}I love you, Jules.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:35.98,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113112,1115982}{\i1}Just a little longer.\NHold out just a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:41.82,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117783,1121821}{\i1}If I was Victor's\Npartner in dance…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:03.97,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142775,1143976}Captain Langlois.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:07.54,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143976,1147546}I regretfully inform that you and your men\Nwill be joining the Paris garrison.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:09.58,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147913,1149582}Yes, General Gambetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:13.78,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150416,1153786}Ladies and gentlemen,\Ncrème de la crème of the French society.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.78,0:19:17.52,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153786,1157523}I am General Gambetta\Nfrom the French Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.52,0:19:19.69,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157523,1159692}We have fallen on hard times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:24.03,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159692,1164030}Our French Army suffered a crushing defeat\Nand surrendered in the Battle of Sedan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:28.10,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164030,1168100}Our Emperor Napoleon III was\Ntaken prisoner by the Prussian army.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:29.73,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168601,1169735}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:30.63,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169735,1170636}I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:32.30,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170636,1172304}How could this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:34.00,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172304,1174006}Silence, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:37.14,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174006,1177143}The Prussian army has started\Nto advance towards Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:40.98,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177143,1180980}Paris is in crisis and needs immediate\Nmobilization of all available forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:52.89,Default,Marie,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190923,1192892}Andréa…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.89,0:19:54.19,Default,Léon,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192892,1194193}Andréa.
